# === 知识库 .gitignore (P1 2026-06-21) ===
# 只跟踪知识文档(.md)与脚本(.py/.js/.sh)，排除大体积工程资料二进制与缓存
# Obsidian附件位置"./"（随文件存放），无集中附件目录可开白名单，图片不纳入git

# --- 大体积工程资料(不入git，单独靠文件系统/备份管理) ---
*.pdf
*.zip
*.rar
*.7z
*.dwg
*.dwf
*.dxf
*.mp4
*.flv
*.avi
*.mov
*.exe
*.dll
*.pyd
*.msi
*.GQI4

# --- 大图片(保留小图标可按需放开) ---
*.jpg
*.jpeg
*.png
*.bmp
*.tif
*.tiff

# --- Office大文件(按需:此处先排除,体积大且常二进制) ---
*.doc
*.docx
*.xls
*.xlsx
*.ppt
*.pptx

# --- 缓存/虚拟环境/平台元数据 ---
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
.venv/
venv/
node_modules/
.obsidian/workspace.json
.obsidian/cache/
.claudian/sessions/
.skillhub-install/
.archive/
crawl_output/
test-output/
output/

# --- Workbuddy 运行时数据(沃巴迪运营部) ---
.workbuddy/memory/
.workbuddy/automations/*/memory.md
.workbuddy/automations/automation-1782290034285/  # 临时调试实例
.obsidian/plugins/obsidian-custom-frames/         # 插件缓存目录

# --- 密钥/凭证(绝对禁止入 git,违反 v3.0 红线 #5) ---
.env
.env.*
*.env
config/.env
config/config.yaml
**/ima-creds/
**/api_key
**/client_id
**/credentials*
**/secrets/

# --- 临时文件 ---
*.tmp
*.log
~$*
Thumbs.db
.DS_Store
